- Update to 0.1.2:
  * Cage now implements the
    wlr-screencopy-unstable-v1,
    xdg-output-unstable-v1.xml,
    wlr-gamma-control-unstable-v1,
    and wlr_export_dmabuf_unstable_v1 protocols.
